  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd 11 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8 ; \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "11 Indian fishermen released; Both boats belong to Govt",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "11 Indian fishermen have been acquitted by a court in Urgavariurai with a ten-year suspended sentence.",
        "On 04th, five people were arrested by the navy who were engaged in illegal fishing activities in a boat.",
        "Similarly, on 11th, 06 people were arrested who were involved in illegal fishing activities in a boat.",
        "In both the cases, the hearing of the case related to the arrestees was held today Friday in Urgavariurai Court.",
        "A simple sentence of 18 months suspended for 10 years was announced. They were released and the two boat owners were found with the detainees and the two boats have been taken into state possession."
      ],
